{"tid":2033213,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"送夠頭未？","createTime":"2020-05-24T13:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:51:33.000Z","uid":58462,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f198ccbf32f845865c056ccdfc5a201451c045e","tid":2033213,"uid":58462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"就算畀人話我係分化撚五毛都想發表下我嘅諗法<br />\n當初反送中我哋行出嚟，去大阪同埋聯署係為咗打中共塊面同佢講大部份香港人都反對，吸引國際注意力同畀機會美國界入，而家美國已經將香港戰線納入埋美中冷戰策略，人哋仲特登等人大過埋先屌9中共搞香港<br />\n我哋目的已達成，到底而家仲上街係為乜？妄想上幾次街就可以助攻美國？除咗送頭之外我諗唔出有咩效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auFVk3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauFVk3e.jpg&h=0a52bd28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30ee3f6826c3fc706ce0eb0df51368c780190ee8","tid":2033213,"uid":137109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2033207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2033207</a> -<br />\n國際戰線長期要人"},{"pid":"9fd054d1d4dbbab6e9435e14d7a2df9b9fc485e8","tid":2033213,"uid":140000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"而家唔少媒體都有報導香港人反國安法再次走上街頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街頭戰線正正同其他戰線相輔相成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次行動固然有改善空間，但卻係不可或缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">得罪講句，一班手足為咗香港不幸被捕，而你嘅一句送頭就係踐踏緊佢地嘅付出</span>"}]}